# Catch - 6331-TNV - 12101-FDK

This is a compatibility patch for:

- [TN's Space Mining and Salvage (6331-TNV)](https://www.nexusmods.com/starfield/mods/6331) by [TheOGTennessee](https://next.nexusmods.com/profile/TheOGTennessee)
	- Permission to patch granted by:
		- [Nexus Mods - Mod Page - Permissions](https://web.archive.org/web/20241215121423/https://www.nexusmods.com/starfield/mods/6331)
	- Donate:

		[![PayPal Badge](https://img.shields.io/badge/PayPal-white?style=flat&logo=paypal&logoColor=black)](https://www.paypal.com/donate?business=TheOGTennessee@gmail.com)
- [Starfield Revised - Skills (12101-FDK)](https://www.nexusmods.com/starfield/mods/12101) by [Samuel181093](https://next.nexusmods.com/profile/samuel181093)
	- Permission to patch granted by:
		- [Nexus Mods - Mod Page - Permissions](https://web.archive.org/web/20241215122940/https://www.nexusmods.com/starfield/mods/12101)
	- Donate:

		[![Ko-fi Badge](https://img.shields.io/badge/Ko--fi-white?style=flat&logo=kofi&logoColor=black)](https://ko-fi.com/samuel181093)
		[![Buy Me A Coffee Badge](https://img.shields.io/badge/Buy_Me_A_Coffee-white?style=flat&logo=buymeacoffee&logoColor=black)](https://buymeacoffee.com/samuel181093)
		[![PayPal Badge](https://img.shields.io/badge/PayPal-white?style=flat&logo=paypal&logoColor=black)](https://www.paypal.com/business=Samuelwhitehead666@hotmail.co.uk)

Both make changes to the geology skill. This compatibility patch merges these so you get the best of both worlds.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> This compatibility patch is an independent creation and is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or officially supported by the original author(s) of the mods involved.

Find more compatibility patches here: [Catch Collection](https://github.com/catch-group/catch-collection)

## Recommended Load Order

1. TN's Space Mining and Salvage
2. Starfield Revised - Skills
3. Catch - 6331-TNV - 12101-FDK
